{"id": 2980, "genre": 1000, "title": "你的“网络失语症”都有啥“病因”？", "description": "说一说吧，为啥你现在都不太爱在网上说话了？", "record_count": 14437, "comment_count": 75, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190610152804qoyxYlHsFfCkz6UZ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-08-27T16:10:42Z", "questions": [{"id": 5871, "title": "你的“网络失语症”都有啥“病因”？", "content": "你的“网络失语症”都有啥“病因”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 345805, "content": "语言能力有限，想回复别人不知道该说什么", "image": "img/option/option/20190610153410Te6BcjlD1CUFYw3q.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345807, "content": "担心不被理解，人的悲欢并不相同", "image": "img/option/option/20190610153701b7M8pkOhEdIVH9XQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345808, "content": "分组疲劳，发个状态得屏蔽七个分组过度麻烦了", "image": "img/option/option/20190610154022VnWs19p3BNqLjfPG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345810, "content": "没啥可说，生活一成不变过一年就像过一天重复364天", "image": "img/option/option/20190610154531pMWC1BLwinH7umtZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345814, "content": "想说的话别人都说过了，想发的照片别人都发过了", "image": "img/option/option/20190610154920mLTpUn216cBHJfAZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345815, "content": "格调担忧，担心发的东西不够高级", "image": "img/option/option/20190610155034Pmzg69T20kYfAM1E.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345816, "content": "对环境失望，曾经信赖的地方一点点被劣币稀释", "image": "img/option/option/201906101551427QdMCTl4zuG2vSe9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345817, "content": "浪费时间，有这功夫不如多看几页书多刷几部电影", "image": "img/option/option/20190610155428IqUGZWnuwxBHcSRz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345843, "content": "没地方发言，可信赖的说话空间消失了", "image": "img/option/option/20190827130425JCPKy9NF4IGXVcUW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345844, "content": "各种过滤各种变词，管理员却还是说有问题", "image": "img/option/option/201908271325017nyWL02dGEYmg9DX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}